Maintainer: Thiyanga Talagala <tstalagala@gmail.com>
Description: The seer package provides implementations of a novel meta-learning framework for forecast model selection using time series features. We call this framework FFORMS (Feature-based FORecast Model Selection). For more details see our paper at https://www.monash.edu/business/econometrics-and-business-statistics/research/publications/ebs/wp06-2018.pdf .
